item.title: I dont have a router, but
item.dc:creator: @Graham Graham
item.description:
@Graham wrote:

No, if you don’t have a router then the connections should be able to get straight through.

Your ISP may be blocking incoming connections. To check put your server up and then go to http://www.whatsmyip.org/ports/ and put 43594 in the custom check. See if it is open, timing out, or closed and post back here.
